15
00:02:00,590 --> 00:02:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}FLOOR MAP OF THE REINWEIß ESTATE
1ST FLOOR</font>

16
00:02:08,780 --> 00:02:14,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Around that time, Kai climbed a ladder 
to meet Diana in the guest room.</font>

17
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:18,400
